snippet.title: Amber Heard wows at Pain and Glory premiere in Cannes
snippet.description:
Bella Hadid and Amber Heard sizzled as they  led the celebrity arrivals at the glittering Cannes Film Festival premiere of Pain and Glory on Friday. The supermodel, 22, and the actress, 33,  commanded attention as they walked the red carpet, clad in couture gowns with statement trains.
